# ⚠ Singleton vs Prototype Bean Lifecycle

## Singleton Bean

Spring manages the complete lifecycle.

```text id="bl19"
Create
   │
   ▼
Initialize
   │
   ▼
Destroy
```

---

## Prototype Bean

Spring creates the Bean but does not manage destruction.

```text id="bl20"
Create
   │
   ▼
Initialize

(No automatic destroy)
```

---

