# ⭐ Advantages of Bean Lifecycle

* Automatic Resource Management
* Proper Initialization
* Automatic Cleanup
* Better Memory Management
* Simplifies Development

---

# ❌ Limitations

* Additional Learning Curve
* Prototype Beans Need Manual Cleanup
* Too Many Lifecycle Hooks Can Increase Complexity

